SUMMARY:Jules O’Brian: Avoid Excessive Cleavage (and Other Advice to Igno
 re)
LOCATION:Camden Comedy Club\, 100 Camden High Street\, London
DESCRIPTION:Now in her fifties\, Jules O’Brian has become a magnet for ad
 vice she never asked for. What to wear. How to behave. How to age “gracef
 ully”. And which inspirational quotes she should apparently be living by.
  She’s not having it. A former English teacher turned stand-up\, Jules ta
 kes aim at the clichés\, unsolicited opinions and well-meaning nonsense th
 at seem to multiply the older you get. From strangers offering life advice 
 to the constant pressure to shrink\, behave and be grateful for it. Warm\, 
 sharp and very funny\, this is a show about getting older\, getting wiser\,
  and deciding which bits of advice can get in the bin.\nMore info: https://
 comedyatlas.app/comedy-atlas/event/jules-obrian-avoid-excessive-cleavage-an
 d-other-advice-to-ignore/
